'''Little Shasta Church''' is a church located in [[Little Shasta, California]].

==History==
In 1875, after a series of meetings, Reverend Roswell Graves organized the church,<ref>{{cite book|title=The Pacific|publisher=J.W. Douglas|date=1909|volume=59}}</ref> then known as Little Shasta Congregational Church,<ref>{{cite book|last=Mord|first=Jeanne|author2=Bette R. Mills |title=Sentinels of Love: Rural Churches of California|publisher=Fithian Press|date=1990|edition=illustrated}}</ref> which was built in 1878.

